    "And <span class=\"person\">David</span> spake to the men that stood by him, saying, What shall be done to the man that killeth this <span class=\"place\">Philistine</span>, and taketh away the reproach from <span class=\"place\">Israel</span>? for who is this uncircumcised <span class=\"place\">Philistine</span>, that he should defy the armies of the living God?",
